- Reducing cognitive load for new users
- Providing single source of truth on each VPS
- Making tools discoverable for agents","status":"in_progress","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-01-25T04:03:24.112845679Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-01T19:17:20.044529688Z","external_ref":"github:Dicklesworthstone/agentic_coding_flywheel_setup#68","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["cli"],"comments":[{"id":349,"issue_id":"beads_rust-lr74","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"## Background: The Flywheel Documentation Problem

